  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Version 1.0.3 is now available for Windows, mac OS, Linux and Steam OS. This version brings minor enhancements to the achievements system.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The peaceful village of Inirea is under attack and needs your help to defend it from monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this family-friendly arcade-style shooter,  you will take command of powerful weapons to defend the village from hordes of monsters, gaining points and powerups as you progress through the maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras/ac9a314dc93ebef235642ac176a8cdbb.avif?t=1755607017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras_big/ac9a314dc93ebef235642ac176a8cdbb.avif?t=1755607017 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game consists of several maps, each with their unique characteristics, weapons and  waves of enemies. Procedurally generated enemies ensure an exciting gaming experience every time you play the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras/9308f085a8c2f07a4bb14ce7715cc921.avif?t=1755607017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras_big/9308f085a8c2f07a4bb14ce7715cc921.avif?t=1755607017 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of the maps will require you to defend multiple bases simultaneously. In maps that have multiple bases, you can click on a base to take control of the base. Any bases that you are not actively controlling will function as automatic towers and will track and fire at the nearest enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several of the larger enemies drop powerups which you can pick up to temporarily upgrade the capabilities of a base. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras/9f700555bd9d35cebda70907b3f8f84d.avif?t=1755607017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras_big/9f700555bd9d35cebda70907b3f8f84d.avif?t=1755607017 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The peaceful village of Inirea is under attack and needs your help to defend it from monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this family-friendly arcade-style shooter,  you will take command of powerful weapons to defend the village from hordes of monsters, gaining points and powerups as you progress through the maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras/ac9a314dc93ebef235642ac176a8cdbb.avif?t=1755607017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras_big/ac9a314dc93ebef235642ac176a8cdbb.avif?t=1755607017 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game consists of several maps, each with their unique characteristics, weapons and  waves of enemies. Procedurally generated enemies ensure an exciting gaming experience every time you play the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras/9308f085a8c2f07a4bb14ce7715cc921.avif?t=1755607017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras_big/9308f085a8c2f07a4bb14ce7715cc921.avif?t=1755607017 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of the maps will require you to defend multiple bases simultaneously. In maps that have multiple bases, you can click on a base to take control of the base. Any bases that you are not actively controlling will function as automatic towers and will track and fire at the nearest enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several of the larger enemies drop powerups which you can pick up to temporarily upgrade the capabilities of a base. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras/9f700555bd9d35cebda70907b3f8f84d.avif?t=1755607017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633790/extras_big/9f700555bd9d35cebda70907b3f8f84d.avif?t=1755607017 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
